ExternalData.Subtitlesect: Extension of the International Coffee Agreement, 1976*

EIF.Label: Entry into force
EIF.Labeltext: 1 October 1982, in accordance with paragraph 2of Resolution No. 318 adopted by the International Coffee Council on 25 September 1981. The Agreement expired in accordance with its provisions on 30 September 1983.

TreatyText.Label: Text
TreatyText.Text: United Nations, Treaty Series, vol. 1291, p. 291; Resolution No. 318 adopted by the International Coffee Council.
